dc_title_s: Shanghai shi shi qu jiao tong tu
dc_description_s: Selected buildings are shown pictorially. Verso: Shanghai shi jiao qu jiao tong tu [Transportation map of Shanghai suburb]. Inset maps: (1) Renmin Gongyuan = [Renmin (People's) Park] -- (2) Zhongshan Gongyuan = [Zhongshan Park] -- (3) Yuyuan = [Yuyuan Garden] -- (4) Hongkou Gongyuan = [Hongkou Park] -- (5) Changfeng Gongyuan = [Changfeng Park] -- (6) Huangpu Gongyuan = [Huangpu Park] -- (7) Xijiao Gongyuan = [Xijiao Park and Zoo] -- (8) Fuxing Gongyuan = Fuxing Park. Includes street index.
